.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bongani, bluemaster, alhambra
City: nizza, venice, boston, hamburg
1. the person traveling to nizza is not to the left of the bluemaster-smoker##8
2. the person traveling to venice is on the far left##1
3. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the bongani-smoker is in an even position##4
5. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left or far right##3
6. the pall-mall-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hamburg##5
7. the alhambra-smoker is the person traveling to boston##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Cigar           | pall-mall | bongani | bluemaster     | alhambra |
| City   | venice    | hamburg   | nizza | boston    |

