.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
House: wooden, townhouse, tower, victorian
4 different pets are kept: cat, turtle, mouse, lizard
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the lizard##1
2. the owner of the cat is not to the left of the owner of the turtle##8
3. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the townhouse house##1
4. the victorian house is not to the right of the owner of the mouse##8
5. the wooden house is the owner of the cat##1
6. the wooden house is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the victorian house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| House   | tower   | townhouse         | victorian   | wooden    |
| Pet         | turtle | lizard | mouse | cat |

