.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, amber, green, black
There are 4 different nationalities: colombian, argentine, american, egyptian
1. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who likes fuchsia and the person who likes amber##7
2. the person who likes green is somewhere to the left of the american##5
3. the person who likes black is somewhere between the person who likes green and the person who likes fuchsia##7
4. the person who likes green is not to the left of the egyptian##8
5. the egyptian is somewhere between the person who likes amber and the argentine##7
6. the argentine is somewhere to the right of the person who likes black##5
7. the argentine is not to the left of the person who likes fuchsia##8
8. the argentine is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | amber   | green | black | fuchsia    |
| Nationality         | colombian | egyptian   | american   | argentine |

