.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-6::.
4 different pets are kept: cat, bird, goldfish, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, skateboard, train
1. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is somewhere to the left of the owner of the cat##5
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left or right of the person driving the skateboard##3
5. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the bird##5
6. the owner of the ferret is not to the left of the person driving the motorbike##8
7. the owner of the ferret is the person driving the motorbike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Pet          | ferret | cat | bird  | goldfish |
| Transport   | motorbike   | train         | skateboard | quad-bike |

