.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
City: hannover, berlin, new-york, miami
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, documentary, scientific, disaster
1. the person watching documentary movies is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
2. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere between the person traveling to miami and the person watching scientific movies##7
3. the person watching scientific movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching crime movies##5
4. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person watching crime movies##8
5. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person traveling to berlin##8
6. the person traveling to hannover is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
7. the person watching crime movies is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
8. the person traveling to hannover is on the left of the person traveling to miami##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| City   | berlin      | new-york | hannover | miami   |
| Movie-Genre      | crime | scientific | disaster  | documentary |

