3. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
4. the owner of the cat is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the person who growsaconite##7
5. the person who growslily is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
6. the person who growszinnia is somewhere between the owner of the pony and the person who growslily##7

