.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, cycling, skateboarding, sailing
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, sudoku, drawing, baking
1. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's hobby is camping##2
2. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is baking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is golf##3
4. the person who's sport is cycling is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is camping##5
5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
6. the person who's sport is skateboarding is not the person who's hobby is drawing##6
7. the person who's sport is sailing is not to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
8. the person who's hobby is camping is not to the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Sport   | sailing   | golf | skateboarding | cycling |
| Hobby     | baking | sudoku       | camping  | drawing    |

