3. the person playing backgammon is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is skateboarding##5
4. the person playing go is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who's sport is soccer is between the person playing canasta and the person playing domino##2
6. the person who's sport is parkour is on the far left##1
7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person playing canasta##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
