.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: filmmaking, fishing, writing, woodworking
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, subway, van, bus
 1. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the left of the person driving the van##5
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##8
 3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person driving the van##1
 4. the person driving the van is not to the right of the person driving the subway##8
 5. the person driving the bus is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 6. the person driving the subway is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
 7. the person driving the subway is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not to the right of the person driving the van##8
 9. the person driving the subway is not to the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##8
10. the person who's hobby is fishing is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Hobby          | fishing    | writing | filmmaking | woodworking |
| Transport   | tram | bus  | van     | subway    |

