.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-17::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, april, march, june
City: boston, liverpool, edinburgh, marseilles
1. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
2. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##8
3. the person traveling to edinburgh is not to the right of the person traveling to liverpool##8
4. the person who's birthday is in march is not the person traveling to marseilles##6
5. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person traveling to marseilles##8
6. the person traveling to boston is on the far right##1
7. the person who's birthday is in march is on the left of the person traveling to marseilles##1
8. the person who's birthday is in march is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |    3     |    4    |
| Birthday           | march | june | april | november   |
| City   | edinburgh       | marseilles      | liverpool    | boston |

