.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, soy-milk, lemonade, tea
4 different pets are kept: horse, frog, guinea-pig, bird
1. the person drinking lemonade is the owner of the horse##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is not to the left of the owner of the frog##8
3. the owner of the frog is the owner of the frog##1
4. the owner of the bird is the person drinking tea##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is between the owner of the frog and the person drinking tea##2
7. the person drinking lemonade is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage    | tea        | soy-milk | cola | lemonade |
| Pet   | bird | guinea-pig | frog   | horse    |

