.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, raspberry, apricot, tomato
There are 4 different favourite colors: green, ebony, blue, amber
1. the person eating tomato is not the person who likes blue##6
2. the person who likes blue is not to the right of the person eating apricot##8
3. the person eating raspberry is somewhere between the person eating apricot and the person eating tomato##7
4. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the right of the person eating pomegranate##5
5. the person who likes ebony is somewhere to the left of the person who likes amber##5
6. the person who likes green is not to the right of the person who likes ebony##8
7. the person eating raspberry is not to the left of the person who likes amber##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Food         | pomegranate  | tomato | raspberry  | apricot  |
| Color   | green | ebony   | amber | blue |

