.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, basketball, skateboarding, baseball
There are 4 different favourite colors: amber, aquamarine, pink, black
1. the person who likes aquamarine is not the person who's sport is cricket##6
2. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person who likes black##1
3. the person who's sport is baseball is not to the left of the person who likes black##8
4. the person who's sport is skateboarding is the person who likes amber##1
5. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere between the person who likes aquamarine and the person who likes amber##7
6. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is cricket##1
7. the person who likes pink is between the person who likes black and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Sport         | basketball    | baseball | cricket | skateboarding |
| Color   | aquamarine | black      | pink     | amber     |

 